## Project Structure (Mono-repo)

```
cafe-digital/
├── backend/          # Laravel REST API
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── Http/Controllers/
│   │   ├── Repositories/       # Repository pattern
│   │   ├── Services/
│   │   └── Models/
│   ├── database/migrations/
│   └── tests/
├── frontend/         # React SPA (Vite)
│   └── src/
│       ├── pages/
│       ├── components/
│       └── api/
└── mobile/           # React Native Expo
    └── app/
        └── (screens)/
```

---

> **Tip:** Start coding the backend API in Week 2 before the frontend in Week 4 — this way the React SPA and Expo app always have real data to consume, making integration straightforward.
